ğŸ§  Business Problem

E-commerce revenue growth depends on:

Retaining customers

Increasing repeat purchase rates

Identifying high-value segments

Detecting churn risk early

This project answers three strategic questions:

Who drives revenue?

Will revenue sustain over time?

Where are we losing growth opportunities?

