ğŸ“¦ Data Pipeline Architecture

Kaggle API configured securely in Google Colab

Dataset downloaded programmatically

Data cleaned and validated in Pandas

Large dataset uploaded to Google Cloud Storage

Loaded into BigQuery for scalable querying

Connected live to Looker Studio

Interactive dashboards built for executive analysis

This ensures:

Reproducibility

Cloud scalability

BI-ready architecture

